headline: Joe Kiani Appointed CEO of Like Minded Labs
summary: Like Minded Labs, a media technology company that empowers creators by transforming how they communicate, has appointed Joe Kiani, Co-Founder of Like Minded Labs, Founder of Masimo and Founder and Executive Chairman of Willow Laboratories the visionary of the digital-health platform Nutu, as its Chief Executive Officer. Additionally, Bob Chapek, former Chief Executive Officer of The Walt Disney Company, joins the company's board of directors.
